text: El Retiro is a corregimiento in Antón District, Coclé Province, Panama. It has a land area of and had a population of 2,303 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 1,801; its population as of 2000 was 1,998. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Coclé Province
